    subgraph U3["Unit 3: Period 3 - 1754 to 1800"]
        U3S1["The Seven Years' War started because of rivalry between empires and disputes over colonial land"]
        U3S2["The British and colonists fought against the French and their Native American allies"]
        U3S3["Benjamin Franklin proposed the Albany Plan of Union to get the colonies to cooperate"]
        U3S4["Britain won the Seven Years' War, and the Treaty of Paris (1763) confirmed it"]
        U3S5["The Proclamation of 1763 banned colonial settlement west of the Appalachian Mountains"]
        U3S6["Britain's massive war debt led them to start taxing the colonies"]
