        U4S3["The Louisiana Purchase (1803) doubled the size of the United States"]
        U4S4["People debated whether Jefferson even had the constitutional power to buy Louisiana"]
        U4S5["Lewis and Clark explored the new western territory from the Louisiana Purchase"]
