    subgraph U5["Unit 5: Period 5 - 1844 to 1877"]
        U5S1["Manifest Destiny was the belief that America was destined to expand across the entire continent"]
        U5S2["Texas was annexed (added to the US) in 1845 as part of westward expansion"]
        U5S3["The Oregon Treaty with Britain set the northern US border at the 49th parallel"]
        U5S4["Americans migrated west on the Oregon, California, and Santa Fe trails"]
